      "id": "PopularPost221683",
      "post_content": "**Digit** covers this card's history well.  \n  \nIt has potential, but it is specialized.  \n  \nPersonally, I could not see a better card to combo with this than [Sigil of the Empty Throne](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sigil of the Empty Throne). For 2 mana you get a 4/4 flying Angel token and set yourself up to cause all sorts of cycling [shock](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=shock) to the enemy. Just awesome.",
      "posted_by": "SliverApocalypse",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost221683\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_post\"><b>Digit</b> covers this card's history well.<br/><br/>It has potential, but it is specialized.<br/><br/>Personally, I could not see a better card to combo with this than <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Sigil of the Empty Throne\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sigil of the Empty Throne\">Sigil of the Empty Throne</a>. For 2 mana you get a 4/4 flying Angel token and set yourself up to cause all sorts of cycling <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"shock\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=shock\">shock</a> to the enemy. Just awesome.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '221683'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy60153\">SliverApocalypse</span>\r\n                                (1/21/2012 7:05:09 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/Left